    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏玩法</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Eat Colors是一款精确的平台跳跃游戏，你不是奔跑和跳跃，而是从一个表面跳到另一个表面，你是一个粘在任何地方的可爱史莱姆。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772180/extras/d6e122a57cc323d2d1540a3cf43869ec.poster.avif?t=1742561311\" width=600 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772180/extras/d6e122a57cc323d2d1540a3cf43869ec.webm?t=1742561311\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772180/extras/d6e122a57cc323d2d1540a3cf43869ec.mp4?t=1742561311\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >机制</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >保持静止可能会让你失去生命！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >除了保持静止，跳到同一个地方或尝试进行过长的跳跃可能会让你死亡！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772180/extras/f7a8f6f87c55d1620e0e6503fa5f9f56.poster.avif?t=1742561311\" width=600 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772180/extras/f7a8f6f87c55d1620e0e6503fa5f9f56.webm?t=1742561311\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772180/extras/f7a8f6f87c55d1620e0e6503fa5f9f56.mp4?t=1742561311\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特点：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >挑战性的游戏玩法</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与大敌人战斗</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >45个关卡</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可爱的史莱姆</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在为时已晚之前，思考、瞄准并跳跃！</p>",
